-- Yale President Levin to Step Down at End of Academic Year
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2012-08-30T13:17:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-30/yale-president-levin-to-step-down-at-end-of-academic-year.html
Yale University  said President
Richard C. Levin plans to step down at the end of the current
academic year, after 20 years of service.  Levin has served longer than any other president currenty
in the Ivy League, Yale said in a statement on its  website .   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
